Create a SimpleDB instance by calling new SimpleDB() after importing it.

```ts
// We start a SimpleDB instance
import { SimpleDB } from "@nshiab/simple-data-analysis";
const sdb = new SimpleDB();
// You can now use sdb for further operations
await sdb.done();
```

Create a new table from the SimpleDB instance using newTable().

```ts
// We start a SimpleDB instance
import { SimpleDB } from "@nshiab/simple-data-analysis";
const sdb = new SimpleDB();
// We create a new table
const table = sdb.newTable();
// You can now use the table for operations
await sdb.done();
```

Load data into the table using loadData with the path to your CSV file.

```ts
// We start a SimpleDB instance
import { SimpleDB } from "@nshiab/simple-data-analysis";
const sdb = new SimpleDB();
// We create a new table
const table = sdb.newTable();
// Load data from a CSV file
await table.loadData("path/to/your/data.csv");
// You can now perform operations on the table
await sdb.done();
```

When finished, call sdb.done() to clean up resources.

```ts
// We start a SimpleDB instance
import { SimpleDB } from "@nshiab/simple-data-analysis";
const sdb = new SimpleDB();
// Perform your operations here
await sdb.done();
```

Create a SimpleDB instance without passing any options, which will use an in-memory database and default settings.
```
import { SimpleDB } from "@nshiab/simple-data-analysis";
// We start a SimpleDB instance
const sdb = new SimpleDB();
// ... perform database operations here ...
// We close everything
await sdb.done();
```

Pass the `file` and `overwrite` options when constructing the SimpleDB instance.
```
import { SimpleDB } from "@nshiab/simple-data-analysis";
// We start a SimpleDB instance with a file and overwrite flag
const sdb = new SimpleDB({
  file: "./mydatabase.duckdb",
  overwrite: true,
});
// ... perform database operations here ...
// We close everything
await sdb.done();
```

Set the `logDuration` option to true when creating the SimpleDB instance.
```
import { SimpleDB } from "@nshiab/simple-data-analysis";
// We start a SimpleDB instance with duration logging enabled
const sdb = new SimpleDB({
  logDuration: true,
